11d-b582-0a4865dd3bcc","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Yesterday I received a letter from Messer Giovanfrancesco asking whether I had any poems composed by the Marchesa di Pescara. Please tell him that I will look, and send him an answer next Saturday, although I am under the impression that I have nothing of hers, as many things were taken when I was ill away from home. When thou hearest of some case of extreme poverty in the house of a noble\u00A0citizen, especially if it be a family where there are\u00A0daughters to be married, I should be glad if thou wouldst inform me thereof, because I would like to help them for the good of my own soul.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c089ceb8-61f3-4e79-9381-6bff20c909d9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":10,"end":10,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"44e509f2-a542-4239-b9f2-9f08b0da4d4e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":35,"end":56,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b83b1971-1407-48f9-b4c8-11b84b97d315","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":73,"end":73,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4071a830-9dd6-464e-b7c2-afa7d361f3b9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":105,"end":123,"value":"e07fcb12-ae2b-4426-ac3f-c8234739bbec","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"68482277-1d0e-40b9-bc25-979cd020e624","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":138,"end":140,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"075cb372-41b6-434f-a3db-be05d947b240","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":147,"end":147,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8ddd4416-12c4-4d27-96dd-f1a3f873d108","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":169,"end":171,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b7419495-9eac-4308-9bca-71e752f94be2","type":"codex/entity-refer